channel.description:
I have absolutely no Idea which section to put this in. I just want to make a tutorial that will help Moparscape programmers. So feel free to post a request and I will try my best to answer your question, or make a tutorial on it. (PLEASE use search button first to make sure a tut/answer isn't already posted!)
@Mod - If you lock/delete this, please tell me where to put it instead.
